  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>本作中所有出场角色均已成年</u></strong><strong>！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>本作中所有游戏内容非ai生成！</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >QQ游戏交流群：479277260</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >制作人b站账号：@<strong>梅涅メネラウス</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492320/extras/9cf9427397bbc24dd549f4b6c7c7fd37.avif?t=1747713610\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492320/extras_big/9cf9427397bbc24dd549f4b6c7c7fd37.avif?t=1747713610 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><u>愿你在此收获亲情，收获友情，收获一切美好。</u></i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><u>新生活是什么？ 妹妹，家人，爱与希望。</u></i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏简介：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >那天，你出生了，就有妹妹。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >那天，父母再婚，天降妹妹。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >那天，小区偶遇，竟是妹妹。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >简直是妹控天堂！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >太好了，是妹妹！我们有救了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >新生活？妹妹？爱？希望？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>会有的。一定都会有的！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >难道不是吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >12w字剧情，多选项多结局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >12张cg，3张q版sd。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >三位可深入了解的角色。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3-4小时游戏体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >数十首原创bgm，和一首人声op。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>主要角色简介：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492320/extras/fcda7ccd7e6805487446efcfea24ebde.avif?t=1747713610\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492320/extras_big/fcda7ccd7e6805487446efcfea24ebde.avif?t=1747713610 width=800 height=800 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><u>芽音绘见璃</u></i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由于主角父母再婚随母亲一同新来的妹妹！性格开朗活泼，亲近主角。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492320/extras/f68f542ff726e3871c32ed85ef2adfad.avif?t=1747713610\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492320/extras_big/f68f542ff726e3871c32ed85ef2adfad.avif?t=1747713610 width=800 height=800 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><u>见藤伊藻泊</u></i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主角自己的双胞胎妹妹！成熟稳重，是可靠的大人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492320/extras/d65e7dbdff6f91d01917ca7b4f0a37c1.avif?t=1747713610\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492320/extras_big/d65e7dbdff6f91d01917ca7b4f0a37c1.avif?t=1747713610 width=800 height=800 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><u>叶荷玲暮罗</u></i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主角在小区闲逛偶遇的少女，也是学校隔壁班的同学。因为年龄小（疑似跳级但已成年）被大家看作妹妹。富有灵性，活泼有深度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>主要玩法：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >点击屏幕推进剧情！当然是文字游戏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在不同的选项间走向不同的结局吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><u>游玩须知！！！：</u></i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作中所有出场角色<strong><u>均已成年</u></strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>角色画风问题与角色自身年龄无关</u>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作中角色台词<u>仅为角色塑造服务，不代表作者立场</u>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作带有一些令人不适的情节，如<strong>少量攻击性词汇，争议性话题的提及，以及可能引起不安的剧情演出场景</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作品中全部背景素材来源于<strong>场景实拍</strong>，并通过ps滤镜转换制成，<strong><u>非ai制作</u></strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><u>本作中一切人物，事件与现实中任何人物，事件，地点均无关联。如有雷同，纯属巧合。</u></i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >**Notice for Playing This Work:**  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- All characters appearing in this work are adults.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- The art style of the characters is unrelated to their actual ages.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- The dialogues in this work serve only for character development and do not reflect the author's views.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- This work contains some potentially uncomfortable content, including a small amount of offensive language, references to controversial topics, and scenes that may cause distress.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- All background materials in this work are derived from real-life scene photography and processed using Photoshop filters; they are not AI-generated.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- All characters and events in this work bear no relation to any real persons, events, or locations. Any resemblance is purely coincidental.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>制作者名单：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >剧本|立绘|CG|UI|音乐|程序：梅涅_Menelaus.A</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作品中全部背景素材来源于场景实拍，并通过ps滤镜转换制成，非ai制作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>本作中所有出场角色均已成年</u></strong><strong>！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>本作中所有游戏内容非ai生成！</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
